  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Localization is mechanically translated and then personally corrected, and the translation may not be accurate</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At some point, you woke up in an empty space surrounded by strange spatial disturbances. You can't remember why you're here, but fortunately, you still remember your name. Subconsciously, you thought you came here with a very important thing to do, but you have forgotten what to do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just when you were at a loss, a young girl with white hair quietly walked up to you and warmly said</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a Roguelike game with equipment construction and character development as its core.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A little bit of action element rogue+survivor mode refers to a more selective space in the early stages of construction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shop to purchase items that enhance abilities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras/efb6f008748eab7a1c18e2e9792b9bc0.avif?t=1763919017\" width=340 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are also three basic options for upgrading</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras/c266e077b423c54352528a0ccbc2540b.avif?t=1763919017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras_big/c266e077b423c54352528a0ccbc2540b.avif?t=1763919017 width=800 height=440 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special room events</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras/be5f6c2781f67847e1094239b2d4b424.avif?t=1763919017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras_big/be5f6c2781f67847e1094239b2d4b424.avif?t=1763919017 width=800 height=406 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, use your hands, pick up the guy, break into the strange world, and quell the chaos here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Localization is mechanically translated and then personally corrected, and the translation may not be accurate</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At some point, you woke up in an empty space surrounded by strange spatial disturbances. You can't remember why you're here, but fortunately, you still remember your name. Subconsciously, you thought you came here with a very important thing to do, but you have forgotten what to do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just when you were at a loss, a young girl with white hair quietly walked up to you and warmly said</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a Roguelike game with equipment construction and character development as its core.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A little bit of action element rogue+survivor mode refers to a more selective space in the early stages of construction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shop to purchase items that enhance abilities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras/efb6f008748eab7a1c18e2e9792b9bc0.avif?t=1763919017\" width=340 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are also three basic options for upgrading</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras/c266e077b423c54352528a0ccbc2540b.avif?t=1763919017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras_big/c266e077b423c54352528a0ccbc2540b.avif?t=1763919017 width=800 height=440 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special room events</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras/be5f6c2781f67847e1094239b2d4b424.avif?t=1763919017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras_big/be5f6c2781f67847e1094239b2d4b424.avif?t=1763919017 width=800 height=406 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, use your hands, pick up the guy, break into the strange world, and quell the chaos here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
